<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.5.3">
<l>neṉṉalpōy varumeṉṟeṉ ṟeṇṇi yirāmaiyeṉmaṉattē pukuntatu</l>
<l>immaik keṉṟiruntē neṟinīr vaḷañceṟuvil</l>
<l>cenneṟ kūḻaivaram porīi yarivār mukatteḻu vāḷaipōy karumpu</l>
<l>annaṟ kāṭaṇaiyu maṇiyāli yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without thinking over and over whether, having gone yesterday,</l>
<l rend="indent">he will come [back], I was thinking</l>
<l>That [your] entering my heart was for this [whole] life,</l>
<l>[My] lord of lovely Āli where vāḷai fish rush to the safe sugarcane thicket,</l>
<l rend="indent">jumping in the faces of the reapers,</l>
<l>Crossing over the border of the fine paddy crop to the fertile fields</l>
<l rend="indent">with high water.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
